title: Amiga music: Psycho - Physical Attraction (A1200🎧Dolbyfied)
description:
"Physical Attraction" by Psycho/Session (Daniel Eriksson), 22th at The Gathering 1997.
Art "Real Eyez" by Zaac (Laurent Samani). Art source http://artcity.bitfellas.org/index.php?a=show&id=21159

Module internal track name is "physical atraction". I assume here that "atraction" is a typo and it's meant to be "attraction".

Made using real A1200 Rev. 1D.4 audio.

Visit my channel for more Amiga music.

title: SID music: Mibri - Black Lipstick (SIDFX 8580 dual mono bx_🎧)
description:
